This utility allows to modify the properties, set up the parameters and transfer
the files on and of the ``Creative Labs NOMAD II MG'' MP3 portable player.

Basic functions include:
	Examine the model and firmware version.
	Examine the memory usage/totals.
	Examine and modify the ``owner''.
	Examine and modify internal clock.
	Examine and modify FM radio presets.
	Format the memory devices.
	Upload the files.
	Download the files.
	Erase the files.
